import React from "react"
import { useFormikContext } from "formik"
import { CardContent, Typography, Box } from "@material-ui/core"
import { Divider } from "@mui/material"

export default function FormReview() {
	const itemsArray = []
	const { values } = useFormikContext()
	itemsArray.push(
		values.firstName,
		values.lastName,
		values.email,
		values.age,
		values.company,
		values.address1,
		values.address1,
		values.address2,
		values.city,
		values.province,
		values.postalcode
	)
	// console.log(values)
	return (
		<CardContent>
			<Box sx={{ display: "flex" }}>
				<Typography variant='h2' style={{ fontSize: "30px" }}>
					Review Details
				</Typography>
			</Box>
			<Box sx={{ margin: "20px" }}>
				{itemsArray.map((item, index) => {
					return (
						<>
							<Typography
								key={index}
								variant='body1'
								style={{ fontSize: "15px" }}>
								First Name: {item}
							</Typography>
							<Divider />
						</>
					)
				})}

				<Divider />
				<Typography variant='body1' style={{ fontSize: "15px" }}>

				</Typography>
